Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======TEXT=======
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.12,0:01:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的家世也無可挑剔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,范烏哲防衛事務交由正規軍的巴貝爾少校負責
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必不辜負達蒙將軍閣下厚望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那裡原為義勇軍監管地區
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任命熟悉當地的人去方為上策吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:01:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是否有些自我膨脹了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算立下過一兩次戰功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但終究是義勇軍 請自重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕羅特上尉 既然求戰慾望如此強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如跑一趟巴裡亞斯沙漠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴裡亞斯沙漠？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那裡毫無戰略價值可言…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有目擊情報稱在那裡發現帝國兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要前往偵查 不要抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順從就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人順從是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好興致啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來如何 格雷戈爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰 說話好刻薄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓 是格雷戈爾 有名的嚴厲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 今天先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.48,0:03:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次補償
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁殿下外出未歸 真逍遙自在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非趁機 我這人平時就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何時拿下范烏哲？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數日內
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你的性格來說夠急的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急欲挽回克羅汀的失利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把人說成是無能之輩一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:04:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮 我只是想說切忌急躁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經的仇敵給你一句忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每逢季節更替 這塊舊傷就會告誡我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能相信黑騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是帝國人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是菲拉爾德人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs32}菲拉爾德：被帝國吞併的小國
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我是否著急 確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要親手收拾那輛坦克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦克？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前還命令人家去送死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.23,0:04:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世上最可怕的就是男人的嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:05:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法容忍義勇軍第三中隊打了一場漂亮仗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 為什麼又是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認賭服輸 掏錢掏錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉魯高 你好壞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是第一小隊裡的年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭博行為是被明令禁止的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必呢 一本正經的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧 大家都是被晾在一邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭麵包房 巴裡亞斯分店開張了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中士你在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有爐子 用鐵鍋試著烤的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.37,0:05:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來雖然一般 味道很香哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭·梅爾姬沃特中士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是麵包師 而是義勇軍士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:05:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是義勇軍士兵 同時也是麵包師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳不離手曲不離口嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 嘗嘗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客氣什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當心長不高喔 拉瑪爾·瓦魯特中士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著你管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是來找隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.49,0:06:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾迪奧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我陪你一起找
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎拉 維爾金在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥沒來過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找的是法爾迪奧·蘭扎特隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是第七小隊隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.66,0:06:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾迪奧和維爾金一起失蹤的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說伊莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個季節維爾金喜歡對什麼進行寫生？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:06:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫生？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼認為？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說是人所為 不如說是偶發的事故
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從考古學角度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我難以贊同你的觀點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縱覽史籍「達魯庫斯之災」顯然是人有意而為
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金 法爾迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護窩蜥蜴找到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼艾麗西婭會知道護窩蜥蜴？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆同時失蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是法爾迪奧陪維爾金去寫生了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名偵探也相形見絀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明平日對我們很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 在意的人是他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 拉瑪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換個地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 大家都是值得信任的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會四處張揚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是什麼同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七小隊缺少作為軍人的自覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了點名 就飄飄然了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 這話怎麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說隊裡還有達魯庫斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我聽下你們的意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於達魯庫斯之災
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我們還在針對達魯庫斯之災的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行嚴肅認真的探討
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 有必要現在談這些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎拉和艾麗西婭 不感覺好奇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在2000年前 發生在腳下這片土地上的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 拉瑪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在正站在歷史事件的現場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴裡亞斯遺跡近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說 此行是為完成偵查任務
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個死板的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只是傳說神話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說那是瞎編的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就大錯特錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有被達魯庫斯人燒燬的城市遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達魯庫斯人焚燒大地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神族人將其擊敗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是歷史上的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到這裡 法爾迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為所謂的「達魯庫斯人燒燬城市」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是事後人們的主觀認為
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 伊莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 如果我生活在當時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會無故把自己的財產付之一炬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你的意思是從邏輯上無法解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:10:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達魯庫斯人自身對災難傳承的缺失也令人不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實有眾多歷史學家對此表示疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎拉辯論起來相當厲害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對自己的論點也有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼伊莎拉 歸根結底…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你們三個無視我和拉瑪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家一起來討論吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽完我們的討論 有什麼想法？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ragnite精煉工廠由於人員不足
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有平日裡五成的產量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達魯庫斯人不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 佔居民總數的三成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得達魯庫斯人在校生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和14歲以下兒童不用動員入伍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們也幹活就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這樣就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ragnite是國家之本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須維持生產量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 義勇軍完成撤退了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 義勇軍只會給正規軍添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要說服維爾金
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 這些都要帶去？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 難得來巴裡亞斯一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有機會實地調查的話 再好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長變了 是因為他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七小隊 那群吊兒郎當不務正業的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我變了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你這麼說 或許是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意范烏哲的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白你的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.03,0:12:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能贏的戰鬥為什麼要眼睜睜的丟掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 高官們個個如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非自己吃到苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則不會醒悟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 你認為能贏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.90,0:12:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是相同意見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴貝爾少校必敗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 拉瑪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士也需要休息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本也需要帶去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,19:00回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會對那種地方感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有考古新發現 必須感謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我也得去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左擁右抱 還不滿意？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…有異樣聲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.05,0:13:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下傷腦筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是汽化器的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這你都能看出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的特長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車程10到15分鐘左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼看快到了 現在放棄讓人不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走也能走過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你們去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡等 和漢斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定能修好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來也可以修啊 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎拉 是因為傳說的緣故嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非在意這些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果有人為此感到不快 還是避免為好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.73,0:14:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是指桑罵槐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.51,0:14:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 等你們回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎拉可固執了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這裡就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我留下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要有人監視是否有敵人出沒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐懼、好奇心與好感 是如此相似
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是說 拉瑪爾很在意伊莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫且不說維爾金
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭怎麼也大驚小怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是很喜歡法爾迪奧嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明這是兩種完全不同的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換言之 艾麗西婭說的「他喜歡法爾迪奧」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屬於狼對狼群首領的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.61,0:15:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是為你才留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:15:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快修好它！不難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.04,0:16:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有光線射入也如此明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為石壁中富含Ragnite的結晶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 據說這裡曾經是採掘場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牆上好像刻有記號
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是古代Northern（北方）文字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不僅是女武神人的聖地 還是圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖書館…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牆上記述的是女武神人與達魯庫斯之災
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 不堪回首的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不堪回首 是對誰而言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對一切而言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神人與達魯庫斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對整個世界 都是不堪回首的愚蠢故事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貪得無厭者將所有家禽果實據為己有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 並憑借其邪法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將巴裡亞斯平原化為焦土
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續讀 賽爾貝莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者大悲 怒而將長矛朝向貪得無厭者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青焰之矛刺穿貪得無厭者的心臟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地從此恢復生機盎然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是達魯庫斯人自己焚燬的城市舊址
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說女武神人建造這座神殿安撫魂靈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為什麼女武神人也滅亡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是擁有神通廣大的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:18:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達魯庫斯之災距今不過2000年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到自然淘汰的話 未免過於短暫了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加利亞公國的大公 蘭蒂格瑞絲家族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說繼承了女武神人的血脈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神人的真相 現在已經成為一個謎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些碑文全部完成解讀的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能解開這個謎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.27,0:18:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 包括達魯庫斯之災的細節在內
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有許多事未被提及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女武神…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚天發現啊 沒想到別有洞天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太驚人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭 你是幸運女神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會發生這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾迪奧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了全新的碑文
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定女武神人之謎也會因此被解開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷史又向前邁進一大步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭…恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾迪奧 稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲早會有被更多人看到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:20:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先睹為快不算為過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不知會發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我別去？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去為好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐等達蒙那樣的老狐狸搶走功勞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒興趣的話 你可以先回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個目睹 這是件很了不起的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 原來傳說的細節在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克西米利安殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 法爾迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我上面寫著什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是伊莎拉她們跟來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問人姓名前 理應先自報家門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======ED=======
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:45.83,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君に会いたくて　夜明けも待たずに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.21,0:21:49.84,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}走り出していた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:55.78,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}思い出は僕を　海辺に導く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.07,0:22:00.67,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今もう一度飛んでみるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:04.95,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}あの風にのって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:15.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}心地良さばかりを　求めて生きていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:19.44,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}ぐるぐる同じ場所で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.51,0:22:25.18,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}そんな僕の前に　現れた笑顔は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:28.91,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}太陽のようだった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:37.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君に会いたくて　夜明けも待たずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:41.48,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}走り出していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:47.14,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}笑い合えるように　唄い合えるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.45,0:22:52.25,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今もう一度飛んでみるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.44,0:22:56.13,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}あの風にのって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:45.83,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}太想見你 不等天明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.21,0:21:49.84,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}就飛奔出門
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:55.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}回憶將我 引向海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.07,0:22:00.67,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此刻真想再次飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:04.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}乘風飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:15.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一味追求安逸的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:19.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}原地踏步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.51,0:22:25.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}出現在我面前的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:28.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}像太陽般燦爛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:37.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}太想見你 不等天明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:41.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}就飛奔出門
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:47.14,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想和你共同歡笑歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.45,0:22:52.25,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此刻真想再次飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.44,0:22:56.13,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}乘風飛翔
